Cell.Data: Sorry, the name %1 is already taken. Please chose another name.
抱歉，名称%1已经被使用。请选择其他名称。
Are you sure you want to delete %1 ? All your items and progression will be lost.
你确定要删除%1？所有物品和进度都会丢失。
造成的特殊状态持续时间
受到的特殊状态持续时间
受到眩晕攻击持续时间
Your maximum Health Points. When they reach 0, you die.
你的最大生命值。当他们到达0时，你就会死亡。
The amount of Health Points you gain each second.
每秒回复的生命值点数。
Your total Strength. Increases your Damage and Critical Damage with Weapons and improve effects like Rage Generation or Stun duration.
你的总力量。增加你的武器伤害和暴击伤害，并提高怒气生成以及眩晕持续时间等特殊状态效果。
Your total Dexterity. Increases your Movement Speed, Dodge Chance and Critical Chance with Weapons.
你的总敏捷。增加你的移动速度，闪避几率和使用武器的暴击几率。
Your total Constitution. Determines your Maximum Health and how you recover from negative effects like Stun or Knock-Down.
你的总体质。确定最大生命值，以及多快从负面效果（如“眩晕”或“击倒”）中恢复。
Your total Power. Determines your Maximum Resource pool and increases Spells Damage and Spells Critical Chance.
你的总能量。确定你的最大资源池，并增加法术伤害和法术暴击几率。
Your total Armor. Reduces part of incoming Physical Damage within your Armor range. Damage points exceeding Armor range aren't affected by this reduction.
你的总护甲。在你的护甲范围内减少受到的部分物理伤害。超过护甲范围的伤害不受此减少影响。
Your total Armor Efficiency. Represents the percentage of incoming Physical Damage within Armor range that is prevented.
你的护甲效率。表示吸收护甲范围内物理伤害的百分比。
The Damage bonus applied to your Spells.
应用于你的法术的伤害加成。
The Casting Speed bonus applied to your Spells.
应用于你的法术的施法速度加成。
Your maximum Resource, in both Umbra and Rage.
你的最大资源，包括本影和怒气。
You natural Rage Loss over time, representing your Umbra Regeneration.
随时间的推移你的怒气损失，同时你的本影回复。
The Delay before Umbra Regeneration restarts after gaining Rage. Rage Conservation is not triggered by spending Umbra or Rage.
在产生怒气后本影再生的延迟时间。怒气保存不会因消耗本影或怒气触发。
The amount of Rage Points generated each time you hit an enemy.
每次你击中敌人时产生的怒气点数。
The amount of Rage Points generated each time you are hit.
每次你被敌人击中时产生的怒气点数。
The Casting Speed bonus applied to your Charged Attacks.
应用于你的蓄力攻击的施法速度加成。
Your total Physical Damage. Physical attacks are affected by target's Armor.
你的总体物理伤害。物理攻击受目标的护甲影响。
Your total Fire Damage. Fire attacks may burn target.
你的总火焰伤害。火焰攻击可能会烧伤目标。
Your total Frost Damage. Frost attacks may Freeze target.
你的总冰霜伤害。冰霜攻击可冻结目标。
Your total Lightning Damage. Lightning attacks may Shock target.
你的总闪电伤害。闪电攻击可能会震慑目标。
Your total Poison Damage. Poison attacks may reduce target's Resistances.
你的总毒素伤害。毒性攻击可能降低目标的抗性。
Your total Critical Chance with Weapons. A Critical hit deals extra Damage and has increased Status Effects Chance.
你的武器总暴击几率。暴击造成额外的伤害，并增加造成特殊状态的几率。
Your total Critical Damage Multiplier with Weapons. Represents the extra amount of Damage of Critical Strikes.
你的武器总暴击伤害倍数。表示暴击的额外伤害。
Your total Critical Chance with Spells. A Critical Spell deals extra Damage.
你的法术总暴击几率。暴击法术造成额外的伤害。
Your total Critical Damage Multiplier with Spells. Represents the extra amount of Damage of Critical Spells.
你的法术总暴击伤害倍数。表示暴击法术的额外伤害。
The total modifier of your Spells Cooldown, increasing or decreasing their total duration.
你的法术冷却时间的总修正值，增加或减少他们的总持续时间。
The total modifier of your Spells Rage Cost, increasing or decreasing total costs.
你的法术怒气消耗的总修正值，增加或减少总消耗量。
The total modifier of your Spells Umbra Cost, increasing or decreasing total costs.
您的法术本影消耗的总修正值，增加或减少总消耗量。
The maximum Range of your equipped Weapon (or the longest if two Weapons are equipped).
你装备的武器的最大范围（如果装备两个武器取最长的）。
The average Physical Damage dealt by your Auto-Dash.
你的自动冲锋造成的平均物理伤害。
The maximum Range of your Auto-Dash.
The amount of Rage Points generated for each enemy hit by your Auto-Dash.
自动冲锋命中的每个敌人生成的怒气总数。
The total modifier of your Auto-Dash Cooldown, increasing or decreasing its total duration.
自动冲锋冷却时间的总修正值，增加或减少其总持续时间。
The total Speed modifier of your Auto-Dash.
你的自动冲锋的总速度修正值。
Your total Thorns Damage. Thorns are Physical Damage inflicted to enemies when they hit you and aren't affected by target's Armor.
你的总荆棘伤害。荆棘是当敌人击中你时受到的物理伤害，不会受到目标的护甲影响。
Your total Armor Piercing, which reduces Armor Efficiency of target.
你的总护甲穿透值，减少目标的护甲效率。
You maximum Stamina. Stamina is mainly used to cast Active Dodge-roll.
你最大的耐力。耐力主要用于进行主动闪避。
The total delay before regenerating one Stamina point. Equals 0 if your Stamina Regeneration is cut.
在再生一点耐力前的总延迟。如果你不能恢复耐力，则为0。
Your Passive Dodge Chance against all attacks types. Dodging an attack will completely ignore its effects.
你被动闪避所有攻击类型的几率。被闪避的攻击将不会造成任何影响。
Your Total Invulnerability time when launching an Active Dodge-roll, during which your Dodge Chance is 100%.
启动主动闪避时的总无敌时间，在此期间你的闪避概率为100％。
Total Speed of your Active Dodge-roll.
Your Passive Block Chance. Blocking an attack will reduce its Damage depending on your Block Efficiency. You can only Block Physical attacks.
你的被动格挡几率。格挡攻击会减少其伤害，取决于你的格挡效率。只能格挡物理攻击。
Your total Block Efficiency. Represents the part of Damage reduction on Blocked attacks.
你的总格挡效率。表示格挡攻击时伤害减少的部分。
The total Protection Angle of your equipped Shield. Attacks taken in this frontal angle when Channeling will always be Blocked.
你装备的盾牌的总保护角度。在此身前此角度下受到的攻击将始终被格挡。
This part of incoming Damage is always prevented.
这部分受到的伤害总是被吸收。
Your total Resistance to Stun. May give you a chance to ignore an incoming Stun effect.
你的总眩晕抗性。给你一定忽略攻击造成的眩晕效果的几率。
Your total Resistance to Knock-back. May give you a chance to ignore an incoming Knock-back effect.
你的总击退抗性。给你一定忽略攻击造成的击退效果的几率。
Your total Resistance to Knock-down. May give you a chance to ignore an incoming Knock-down effect.
你的总击倒抗性。给你一定忽略攻击造成的击倒效果的几率。
Your total Stun Chance with Physical attacks. Stun effect prevents targets from acting or moving.
你物理攻击造成眩晕效果的总几率。眩晕效果可阻止目标攻击或移动。
Your total Burning Chance with Fire attacks. Burn effect deals Fire Damage over time to targets.
你火焰攻击造成燃烧效果的总几率。燃烧效果随着时间对目标造成火焰伤害。
Your total Freezing Chance with Frost attacks. Freeze effect prevent targets from acting or moving and make them vulnerable.
你冰霜攻击造成冻结效果的总几率。冻结效果防止目标行动或移动，并使他们更脆弱。
Your total Shocking Chance with Lightning attacks. Shock effect Deals Lightning Damage to surrounding targets and may stun them.
你闪电攻击造成震荡效果的总几率。震荡效果对周围目标造成闪电伤害，并可能使他们眩晕。
Your total Knock-down Chance. Knock-down effect expulses targets on the ground and briefly prevent them from getting up.
你的总击倒几率。击倒效果可以击倒地面上的目标，并短时间防止它们站起。
Your total Knock-back Chance. Knock-back effect physically repels targets and may knock-them down afterwards.
你的总击退几率。击退效果可以让目标后退，并可能被击倒。
Your total Open-Wounds Chance modifier, increasing or decreasing your probability of causing Open-Wounds. Open-Wounds deal Bleeding Damage over time to targets.
你的总创伤几率修正值，增加或减少造成创伤的可能性。创伤随时间造成流血伤害。
Your total Open-Wounds Damage modifier, increasing or decreasing the Damage dealt by your Open-Wounds.
你的总创伤伤害修正值，增加或减少你创伤效果所造成的伤害。
The total Duration modifier of all inflicted effects, such as Burning, Poisoning or Bleeding.
所有造成效果的总持续时间修正值，例如燃烧，中毒或出血。
The total Duration modifier of received effects, such as Burning, Poisoning or Bleeding.
所有受到效果的总持续时间修正值，例如燃烧，中毒或出血。
The total Resistances Reduction applied on Poisoned targets.
对中毒目标造成的总抗性降低。
The total Duration modifier of inflicted Stun effects.
造成的眩晕效果的总持续时间修正值。
The total Duration modifier of inflicted Burning effects.
造成的燃烧效果的总持续时间修正值。
The total Duration modifier of inflicted Freezing effects.
造成的冻结效果的总持续时间修正值。
The total Damage modifier of inflicted Shocking effects.
造成的震荡效果的总伤害修正值。
The total Duration modifier of received Stun effects.
受到的眩晕效果的总持续时间修正值。
The total Duration modifier of inflicted elemental effects (Burning, Freezing and Shocking only).
造成的元素效果的总持续时间修正值（仅限燃烧，冻结和震荡）。
The total auto-picking radius of Globes.
球体的总自动拾取半径。
Your total Gold Find modifier. Increases the amount of looted Gold.
你的总黄金掉落修正值。增加获得的黄金的数目。
Your total Magic Find modifier. Increases the probability of looting Magic Items.
你的总魔法物品掉落修正值。增加获得魔法物品的概率。
The total Cleave Factor of your Melee attacks. Cleaving attacks will hit several enemies beyond your first target and deal reduced Damage to them.
近战攻击的总劈裂系数。劈裂攻击会击中你的第一个目标之外的几个敌人，并对他们造成少量伤害。
The total Cleave Angle Bonus of your Melee attacks (added to the base value of Skills). Combined with Weapon range, it will determine which targets are hit by Cleaving attacks.
近战攻击的总劈裂角度。结合武器范围，它将确定哪些目标被受到劈裂攻击。
The total modifier of your Potions Cooldown, increasing or decreasing their usage frequency.
你的药剂冷却时间的总修正值，增加或减少它们的使用频率。
The total modifier of your Potions Refill-time, increasing or decreasing the delay before they replenish.
你的药剂补充时间的总修正值，增加或减少他们补充之前的延迟。
The total modifier of the Healing capacity of your Healing Potions.
你的治疗药水的治疗能力的总修正值。
Your total Resistance to Physical attacks. Reduces part of all incoming Physical Damage.
你对物理攻击的总抗性。减少部分受到的物理伤害。
Your total Resistance to Fire attacks. Reduces part of all incoming Fire Damage.
你对火焰攻击的总抗性。减少部分受到的火焰伤害。
Your total Resistance to Frost attacks. Reduces part of all incoming Frost Damage.
你对冰霜攻击的总抗性。减少部分受到的霜冻伤害。
Your total Resistance to Lightning attacks. Reduces part of all incoming Lightning Damage.
你对闪电攻击的总抗性。减少部分受到的闪电伤害。
Your total Resistance to Umbra attacks. Reduces part of all incoming Umbra Damage.
你对本影攻击的总抗性。减少部分受到的本影伤害。
Your total Resistance to Sacred attacks. Reduces part of all incoming Sacred Damage.
你对神圣攻击的总抗性。减少部分受到的神圣伤害。
Your total Resistance to Shadow attacks. Reduces part of all incoming Shadow Damage.
你对暗影攻击的总抗性。减少部分受到的暗影伤害。
Your total Resistance to Bleeding attacks. Reduces part of all incoming Bleeding Damage.
你对流血攻击的总抗性。减少部分受到的流血伤害。
Your total Resistance to Poison attacks. Reduces part of all incoming Poison Damage.
你对毒素攻击的总抗性。减少部分受到的毒素伤害。
Your total Resistance to Spells. Reduces part of all incoming Spell Damage.
你对法术抗性的总抗性。减少部分受到的法术伤害。
